# centos安装python3

## 1. 下载python3源码包
- `wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.7.1/Python-3.7.1.tgz`

## 2. 安装依赖
- `yum install gcc zlib-devel libffi-devel openssl-devel`

## 3. 解包 Python-3.7.1.tgz
- `tar -xvzf Python-3.7.1.tgz`

## 4. 进入解压目录
- `cd Python-3.7.1`

## 5. 执行如下命令
- `./configure`
- `make`
- `make install`
